@startuml
autonumber
skinparam style strictuml
skinparam roundcorner 8
skinparam sequenceMessageAlign center

' Color Palette: Ocean Blue & Mint (Professional .NET Style)
skinparam sequence {
    ArrowColor #2E4053
    LifeLineBorderColor #2E4053
    ParticipantBackgroundColor #D6EAF8
    ParticipantBorderColor #2E4053
    BoxBackgroundColor #F4F6F7
}

box "Presentation (Client)" #EBF5FB
    actor "Customer" as User #AED6F1
    participant "Frontend UI" as UI #AED6F1
end box

box "Logic Layer (.NET Core)" #D5F5E3
    participant "BookingController" as API #82E0AA
    participant "BookingService" as Service #82E0AA
    participant "SignalR Hub" as Hub #2ECC71
end box

box "Data Layer (Persistence)" #FADBD8
    participant "EF Core (SQL Server)" as DB #EC7063
end box

== 1. Availability Check ==
User -> UI: Choose Service & DateTime
UI -> API: GET /api/v1/bookings/check-slots
API -> Service: GetAvailableSlots(date)
Service -> DB: Query Available Technicians
DB --> Service: Data List
Service --> API: AvailableSlotsDTO
API --> UI: Display Slots to User

== 2. Booking Execution ==
User -> UI: Click "Confirm Booking"
UI -> API: POST /api/v1/bookings (BookingData)
activate API #82E0AA
API -> Service: CreateBooking(dto)
activate Service #82E0AA
Service -> DB: INSERT INTO Bookings (Status=Pending)
DB --> Service: New Booking ID
Service -> Hub: NotifyNewBooking(adminId, bookingId)
Hub -> "Admin UI": broadcast("New Appointment Alert")
note right #FCF3CF: Real-time via SignalR
Service --> API: Success Result
deactivate Service
API --> UI: 201 Created
deactivate API

UI --> User: Show Confirmation & SMS Sent
@enduml